Dated: 2022-01-13
To:
Property Owner or Reputed Owner:
Original Contractor:
REFUGIO STREET LIMITED PARTNERSHIP
818 S FLORES ST
SAN ANTONIO, TX 78204
Project Information
Project Name:
100 LABOR STREET APARTMENTS
Project Location:
300 LABOR St SAN ANTONIO, TX 78210
Hiring Party:
Ranger Concrete
Please be advised that the undersigned Claimant has an unpaid claim for labor and/or materials furnished according
to a contract or agreement with the above-identified Hiring Party pertaining to the construction project above-
referenced as the Project Name and Project Location. There remains an unpaid balance at this time in the amount of
$8,174.00
The unpaid balance is for work done and/or material furnished during the below listed Month(s):
2021-11
A general statement of the kind of work done and/or materials furnished by Claimant during the above listed Month(s) is:
Rebar and Supplies
The purpose of this letter is to comply with the Mechanics and Materialman's Lien Statutes. If you are not the Original
Contractor or Property Owner on this construction project please contact us.
Cont. on Next Page.
